{"tid":494374,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"9日慕尼黑行程求評","createTime":"2017-12-09T14:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T14:22:26.000Z","uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"40396dbd29798e476ea6784996b469b92e0c064c","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"2月19 - 2月27日<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 晚上10點到慕尼黑 -&gt; 訓教<br />\nDay 2: 早上出發到貝希特斯加登 (應該12點到) -&gt; 得番半日上耶勒峰 <br />\nDay 3: 國王湖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay 4: 藍紹 -&gt; 坐車番慕尼黑<br />\nDay 5: 集中營、德意志博物館<br />\nDay 6: 慕尼黑 -&gt; 楚格峰 -&gt; 慕尼黑<br />\nDay 7: 慕尼黑 -&gt; 新天鵝堡 -&gt; 慕尼黑<br />\nDay 8: 市內觀光? (待定)<br />\nDay 9: 市內觀光 -&gt; 晚上十點坐飛機<br />\n<br />\nDay 10: 早上5點到莫斯科 -&gt; 市區觀光 -&gt; 晚上8點回港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家覺得有無D咩其他景點推介下<br />\n主要想replace Day 7 同 Day 8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f352fa7d07add3180f7c6618ba721e357471b10b","tid":494374,"uid":3135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"國王湖要留意冬天有無封到上湖 夏天去過好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過走個陣大雨到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ad806fb700d331e8b0ed5d0b8d56f52675babe","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國王湖要留意冬天有無封到上湖 夏天去過好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過走個陣大雨到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有research 過<br />\n封左都無計<br />\n照去唯有唔遊上湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f09f413e7576a15beb