at (其實obertrun 都唔差)<br />\n2日 salazbrug<br />\n其餘慕尼黑 國王湖 新天餓堡都有去<br />\n<br />\n國王湖 搭去尾果個湖 預返行一個鐘去木屋 最靚</blockquote><br />\n我去完藍紹再去 1日salazbrug 同 1日 hallastat 再番 慕尼黑?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n2日岩岩好replace 到 Day 7 同 Day 8"},{"pid":"ad13d94e60549358f400296574c4f5bccadf39de","tid":494374,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"國王湖附近魔法森林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47155fbff7e4451d493008a0b0cbccea0cd29318","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CHING坐咩AIRLINE?<br />\n我果幾日都去,但未買機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯航空<br />\n我公司放新年假放幾耐下<br />\n見到4800蚊機票狗沖左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae50a50ef647136a8fc642c3845bb6c391f9c1b3","tid":494374,"uid":4309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12日<br />\n3日 布拉格 ck<br />\n1日 hallastat (其實obertrun 都唔差)<br />\n2日 salazbrug<br />\n其餘慕尼黑 國王湖 新天餓堡都有去<br />\n<br />\n國王湖 搭去尾果個湖 預返行一個鐘去木屋 最靚</blockquote><br />\n冬天無得入內湖,去唔到木屋度,好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a726455fb7b2b89b9f7c78db92f9da87153f3da","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國王湖附近魔法森林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDay 4 去藍紹會去埋阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893f6e8a14866497599edc3f34fe1b16ecaaefdf","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>12日<br />\n3日 布拉格 ck<br />\n1日 hallastat (其實obertrun 都唔差)<br />\n2日 salazbrug<br />\n其餘慕尼黑 國王湖 新天餓堡都有去<br />\n<br />\n國王湖 搭去尾果個湖 預返行一個鐘去木屋 最靚</blockquote><br />\n冬天無得入內湖,去唔到木屋度,好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不要再說了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cdb8aff46e6940a724bb4909d0928539ea9ff3","tid":494374,"uid":4309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CHING坐咩AIRLINE?<br />\n我果幾日都去,但未買機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯航空<br />\n我公司放新年假放幾耐下<br />\n見到4800蚊機票狗沖左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇左咁耐都係得俄航係平,但之前個FD坐過,人到左歐洲,件行李仲係俄羅斯,等左4,5日先送返過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋好似轉機排好耐,D人話轉機時間預係2個鍾以上好D<br />\nD海關手腳好慢"},{"pid":"15a6c2e98917aa301b8dbd8b1196d986b3b5c833","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CHING坐咩AIRLINE?<br />\n我果幾日都去,但未買機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯航空<br />\n我公司放新年假放幾耐下<br />\n見到4800蚊機票狗沖左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇左咁耐都係得俄航係平,但之前個FD坐過,人到左歐洲,件行李仲係俄羅斯,等左4,5日先送返過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋好似轉機排好耐,D人話轉機時間預係2個鍾以上好D<br />\nD海關手腳好慢</blockquote><br />\n我揹個50L背包應該唔洗寄倉<br />\n唔過10KG的話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cda6c88a8584e349be48c5445d73028aee5624e","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"Day 1: 晚上10點到慕尼黑 -&gt; 訓教<br />\nDay 2: 早上出發到貝希特斯加登 (應該12點到) -&gt; 得番半日上耶勒峰<br />\nDay 3: 國王湖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDay 4: 藍紹 -&gt; Salzberg Hbf<br />\nDay 5: Salzberg Hbf (一日遊)<br />\nDay 6: Salzberg Hbf -&gt; Hallsatt -&gt; Salzberg Hbf -&gt; 慕尼黑<br />\nDay 7: 集中營、德意志博物館<br />\nDay 8: 慕尼黑 -&gt; 楚格峰 -&gt; 慕尼黑<br />\nDay 9: 市內觀光 -&gt; 晚上十點坐飛機<br />\n<br />\nDay 10: 早上5點到莫斯科 -&gt; 市區觀光 -&gt; 晚上8點回港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n改成咁樣? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bfa3fd0dbc14dd4f240755f3bd2c4756cf78fb","tid":494374,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>國王湖要留意冬天有無封到上湖 夏天去過好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過走個陣大雨到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇左 四月中先有船上去 冬天去到洋蔥教堂就要折返</blockquote><br />\n不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔洗灰嘅 記得個陣去到真係好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打仲去左邊D景點<br />\n分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個陣尾站慕尼黑 唔係去左好多地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係市內 博物館 集中營 國王湖<br />\n有間食豬手同德國腸幾正 Lunch去食都係十幾歐<br />\n叫Haxnbauer<br />\n不過慕尼黑退稅有啲煩<br />\n預鬆啲時間去機場同睇定要去邊到退稅<br />\ncheck in完 帶埋啲行李去海關 海關stamp完會直接幫你寄倉<br />\n你再去返退稅個到交form</blockquote><br />\nOh 原來你尾站莫斯科 咁可能唔同</blockquote><br />\n 莫斯科唔係歐盟 退稅要係慕尼黑搞"},{"pid":"d361f21b3b5feedeec35402bd2ff49a7a4dd8ef1","tid":494374,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:45:15.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"8182e37c18b6ae194dae82a43f03168dee494076","tid":494374,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"達豪集中營一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06fae30cb58128de86d1bc4ea01f0dffc10cc65","tid":494374,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T18:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>達豪集中營一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去果陣仲要落雨，陰風陣陣好撚寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a728066a85d9004247d347b784f5b65fffd5fd6","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:24:38.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704671865c6606bc3b3857acdcf28ee44f6eb654","tid":494374,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>達豪集中營一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去果陣仲要落雨，陰風陣陣好撚寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567751bf32c00525ca1601e356f1954a9be7bee2","tid":494374,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>達豪集中營一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去果陣仲要落雨，陰風陣陣好撚寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好拿詳細 <br />\n要睇既話睇成日 <br />\n冇心機睇晒.."},{"pid":"6a41bd82e81392c5f2832814b60b51c4be17d71d","tid":494374,"uid":34463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"係慕尼黑WH 緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n凍到唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打去新天鵝堡記得上網BOOK 定飛, 去到WALK IN買飛排好耐"},{"pid":"a78af0b01af771d5d2f2f